### ✅ DO: Implemente retry policies com Polly

```csharp
// ✅ CORRETO - Retry com exponential backoff
private readonly AsyncRetryPolicy _retryPolicy = Policy
    .Handle<Exception>()
    .WaitAndRetryAsync(
        retryCount: 3,
        sleepDurationProvider: retryAttempt => 
            TimeSpan.FromSeconds(Math.Pow(2, retryAttempt)),
        onRetry: (exception, timeSpan, retryCount, context) =>
        {
            _logger.LogWarning(
                exception,
                "Retry {RetryCount}/3 after {Delay}s",
                retryCount,
                timeSpan.TotalSeconds);
        });

await _retryPolicy.ExecuteAsync(async () =>
{
    await _orderRepository.UpdateOrderStatusAsync(orderId, OrderStatus.Completed);
});

// ❌ INCORRETO - Retry manual difícil de manter
for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++)
{
    try
    {
        await _orderRepository.UpdateOrderStatusAsync(orderId, OrderStatus.Completed);
        break;
    }
    catch
    {
        if (i == 2) throw;
        await Task.Delay(1000 * (i + 1));
    }
}
```

